+ "%mini.window.xpm%&Scroll&Bar (75%% scr)" Module FvwmScroll 75p 75p
+ "" Nop
+ "&Arrange Icons%mini.icons.xpm%" All (CurrentDesk Iconic) RecaptureWindow
+ "&Refresh Screen%mini.ray.xpm%" Refresh

